data.description: Look into the Montana Veterans' Home Loan Program as an option for financing, is a fixed-rate, 30-year mortgage loan at 1% lower than the Fannie Mae Daily Historical Yields (FNMA) interest rate! Situated on a just under 14,000 square foot lot, this lovely home has 1,105 square feet of comfortable living space. As you enter the property, you are greeted by a cozy living room that invites you to relax and unwind. The home features 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom, perfect for anyone looking for a cozy retreat. The bedrooms are well-sized, with windows that can provide plenty of natural light. In addition to the main house, this property also includes a detached garage, providing parking and additional storage space. The large backyard is perfect for outdoor activities, gardening, or enjoying a peaceful summer evening with family and friends. Don't miss out on this unique opportunity to own a historic home in a charming town. Being sold as is by a 100% disabled veteran. RECENT PRICE DROP, MOTIVATED SELLER. Look into the Montana Veterans' Home Loan Program as an option for financing! Being sold as is by a 100% disabled veteran. This is for a limited time only, before the price will return to $265,600.
